4 c. An individual conducting surveillance or photographing another individual or
5 another individual's real property, whether owned or rented, with that individual's
6 consent.
7 d. An individual photographing an event open to the public.
8 3. An individual who violates this section is guilty of a class A misdemeanor .
9 Harassment by robot - Livestock and wildlife - Penalty .
10 1. An individual may not intentionally or recklessly harass livestock with a robot. An
11 individual who violates this subsection is guilty of a class B misdemeanor .
12 2. An individual who harasses livestock with a robot, causing physical injury or death to
13 livestock, is guilty of a class A misdemeanor .
14 3. An individual may not intentionally harass wildlife with a robot. An individual who
15 violates this subsection is guilty of a class B misdemeanor .
